Schedule in brief

06 April

  • Crew arrives. Loads gear on R/V Daiber.

07 April

  • 06:00 Arrive at R/V Daiber
  • 06:30 - 13:40 eDNA sampling and mooring retrieval and redeployment for sites T-3C, T-2C, MBON5, MBON4, and A-5C. MPT crew filming field work during cruise and will stop by RTWB.

08 April

  • 06:00 Arrive at R/V Daiber
  • 06:30 - NA eDNA sampling and mooring retrieval and redeployment for sites MBON3, MBON2, T-1C, and MBON1.
